      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h1&gt;Траблшутинг серверов Linux&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ниже приведены команды для анализа сервера в той или иной ситуации.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Состояние дисков&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;состояние-дисков&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d1%81%d0%be%d1%81%d1%82%d0%be%d1%8f%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%b5-%d0%b4%d0%b8%d1%81%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%b2&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Проверка оставшегося места на жестких дисках&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;проверка-оставшегося-места-на-жестких-дисках&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b5%d1%80%d0%ba%d0%b0-%d0%be%d1%81%d1%82%d0%b0%d0%b2%d1%88%d0%b5%d0%b3%d0%be%d1%81%d1%8f-%d0%bc%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82%d0%b0-%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d0%b6%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82%d0%ba%d0%b8%d1%85-%d0%b4%d0%b8%d1%81%d0%ba%d0%b0%d1%85&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;df -h &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Можно сделать alias df=&amp;#34;df -h&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Если надо в inode:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;df -i&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Проверка сколько места занимает тот или иной файл&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;проверка-сколько-места-занимает-тот-или-иной-файл&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%b5%d1%80%d0%ba%d0%b0-%d1%81%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%bb%d1%8c%d0%ba%d0%be-%d0%bc%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82%d0%b0-%d0%b7%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b8%d0%bc%d0%b0%d0%b5%d1%82-%d1%82%d0%be%d1%82-%d0%b8%d0%bb%d0%b8-%d0%b8%d0%bd%d0%be%d0%b9-%d1%84%d0%b0%d0%b9%d0%bb&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Команда ниже, например, выводит информацию обо всех файлах в /tmp.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo du -h /tmp/*&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Анализ жестних дисков(которые ни Nvme, ни SSD)&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;анализ-жестних-дисковкоторые-ни-nvme-ни-ssd&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%b0%d0%bd%d0%b0%d0%bb%d0%b8%d0%b7-%d0%b6%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%82%d0%bd%d0%b8%d1%85-%d0%b4%d0%b8%d1%81%d0%ba%d0%be%d0%b2%d0%ba%d0%be%d1%82%d0%be%d1%80%d1%8b%d0%b5-%d0%bd%d0%b8-nvme-%d0%bd%d0%b8-ssd&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Для этого используются Self-Monitoring, Analysis and Reporting Technology, или по-простому SMART.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt-get install -y smartmontools
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo smartctl -a /dev/sdb&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Утилиту smartctl можно использовать и на NVme, SSD дисках, но там будут использоваться не SMART-контракты.
Так как их нету у такого типа дисков, утилита просто соберет информацию, которой обладает система.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Просмотр информации о raid-ах&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;просмотр-информации-о-raid-ах&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%be%d1%81%d0%bc%d0%be%d1%82%d1%80-%d0%b8%d0%bd%d1%84%d0%be%d1%80%d0%bc%d0%b0%d1%86%d0%b8%d0%b8-%d0%be-raid-%d0%b0%d1%85&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Нужную информацию о raid-ах можно узнать командой ниже:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;cat /proc/mdstat&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Нагрузка на CPU, RAM, диски&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;нагрузка-на-cpu-ram-диски&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%bd%d0%b0%d0%b3%d1%80%d1%83%d0%b7%d0%ba%d0%b0-%d0%bd%d0%b0-cpu-ram-%d0%b4%d0%b8%d1%81%d0%ba%d0%b8&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Для начала надо установить необходимые пакеты.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo apt-get install -y sysstat iotop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Нагрузка на диски&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;нагрузка-на-диски&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%bd%d0%b0%d0%b3%d1%80%d1%83%d0%b7%d0%ba%d0%b0-%d0%bd%d0%b0-%d0%b4%d0%b8%d1%81%d0%ba%d0%b8&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Тут есть две команды, которые надо знать iostat и iotop.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;iostat&lt;/strong&gt; - используется для вывода информации о загруженности диска.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;iotop&lt;/strong&gt; - выводит информацию о процессах, что взаимодействуют с диском.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;iostat
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo iotop&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Утилита top&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;утилита-top&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d1%83%d1%82%d0%b8%d0%bb%d0%b8%d1%82%d0%b0-top&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;%CPU(s) - режимы работы процессора(us - пользовательский режим, system - для ядра, nice - процессы с измененным приоритетом, idle - простой, wait - ожидание завершения I/O, hardware и software - прерывания, steel - украденное время гипервизором)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load Average - показывает среднее время выполнения процессов, а также ввода/вывода&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Память&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;память&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%bf%d0%b0%d0%bc%d1%8f%d1%82%d1%8c&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Всю информацию о памяти можно посмотреть в файле /proc/meminfo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Также можно использовать:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;free -m&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;vmstat&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;top&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Процессы&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;процессы&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#%d0%bf%d1%80%d0%be%d1%86%d0%b5%d1%81%d1%81%d1%8b&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Чтобы просмотреть все процессы можно использовать команду ниже:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

